<li><a href="http://www.newyorker.com/reporting/2009/04/06/090406fa_fact_hersh" class="external text" title="http://www.newyorker.com/reporting/2009/04/06/090406fa_fact_hersh" rel="nofollow">"Syria Calling"</a> — The Obama Administration’s chance to engage in a Middle East peace, <i>The New Yorker</i>, April 6, 2009 issue</li>
</ul>
<p><br /></p>
